{"id": "914329", "revid": "32045548", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=914329", "title": "Militant Chieftain", "text": "Militant Chieftain is a &lt;a href=\"Creatures%20%28Legends%29\"&gt;creature&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"card\"&gt;card&lt;/a&gt; in .\nStrategy.\nMilitant Chieftain is one of several Orc cards that is only effective when used with other Orcs. The relatively high magicka cost, coupled with its relatively weak health and power, make Militant Chieftain unsuitable for a standard Warrior deck. Orcs, however, receive a significant boost from Militant Chieftain, and the random Orc can be a major boon, especially for players running short on cards. Militant Chieftain is a must for Orc decks, but is too niche to be of much value to most Warrior decks."}
