{"id": "121977", "revid": "44356307", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=121977", "title": "Milk", "text": "Milk is a &lt;a href=\"Caves%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;cave&lt;/a&gt; in . The entrance of the cave is located along the western side of the mountains in the &lt;a href=\"West%20Gash%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;West Gash&lt;/a&gt; region, just west of &lt;a href=\"Ald%27ruhn%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Ald'ruhn&lt;/a&gt;. From Ald'ruhn simply follow the road west until entering the West Gash region, the road will curve south. At the first intersection turn right and right again.\nCharacters.\nOther inhabitants of the cave include his guards, who have accompanied him and now they prey upon travelers passing by. These are hostile until the completion of quest below.\nQuests.\n&lt;a href=\"The%20Mad%20Lord%20of%20Milk\"&gt;The Mad Lord of Milk&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe Nerevarine, having joined &lt;a href=\"House%20Redoran\"&gt;House Redoran&lt;/a&gt; will be sent by &lt;a href=\"Athyn%20Sarethi\"&gt;Athyn Sarethi&lt;/a&gt; to solve the issue caused by the \"Mad Lord of Milk,\" &lt;a href=\"Arethan%20Mandas\"&gt;Arethan Mandas&lt;/a&gt;. The Nerevarine may simply kill him, although speaking to him will reveal that he is mad. The Nerevarine may speak to Mandas' father, &lt;a href=\"Llerar%20Mandas\"&gt;Llerar Mandas&lt;/a&gt;, who will ask that the Nerevarine free his granddaughter, &lt;a href=\"Delyna%20Mandas\"&gt;Delyna Mandas&lt;/a&gt;, from &lt;a href=\"Tel%20Fyr%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Tel Fyr&lt;/a&gt;.\nItems.\nAll the crates and chests are lootable without repercussions, even if all the guards are still alive.\nVirtually all items of note in the cave are found on the inhabitants. These objects range from &lt;a href=\"Steel%20Armor%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;steel armor&lt;/a&gt; to &lt;a href=\"Ebony%20Cuirass%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;ebony cuirasses&lt;/a&gt;, although two &lt;a href=\"Orcish%20Armor%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Orcish armor&lt;/a&gt; pieces can be found in a trapped chest next to Mandas."}
