{"id": "17257", "revid": "25356303", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=17257", "title": "Bruma Caverns", "text": "Bruma Caverns is a &lt;a href=\"Locations%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;location&lt;/a&gt; just west of &lt;a href=\"Bruma%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Bruma&lt;/a&gt;. The caverns are connected to &lt;a href=\"Jearl%27s%20House\"&gt;Jearl's House&lt;/a&gt; in Bruma. There are a few &lt;a href=\"Mudcrab%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;mudcrabs&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Rat%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;rats&lt;/a&gt; in this cave, but very little else.\nQuests.\n&lt;a href=\"Spies%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Spies&lt;/a&gt;.\n&lt;a href=\"Mythic%20Dawn\"&gt;Mythic Dawn&lt;/a&gt; agents have discovered the location of &lt;a href=\"Martin%20Septim%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Martin&lt;/a&gt; and are spying on activity in &lt;a href=\"Cloud%20Ruler%20Temple%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Cloud Ruler Temple&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;a href=\"Captain%20Steffan\"&gt;Captain Steffan&lt;/a&gt; and his men have noted their activities, and these spies must be eliminated before they take action."}
