{"id": "897081", "revid": "17401442", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=897081", "title": "Buffs", "text": "Buffs are a term used in MMOs to describe certain effects that abilities use.\nIn terms of , this term was used more formally, with &lt;a href=\"Skills%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Skills&lt;/a&gt; being redesigned and overhauled with &lt;a href=\"Update%206\"&gt;Update 6&lt;/a&gt;' introduction of both the &lt;a href=\"Justice%20System\"&gt;Justice System&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Champion%20System\"&gt;Champion System&lt;/a&gt;.\n&lt;a href=\"Minor%20Aegis\"&gt;Minor Aegis&lt;/a&gt;.\nTake 5% less &lt;a href=\"Damage%20%28Online%29\"&gt;damage&lt;/a&gt; from &lt;a href=\"Group%20Dungeons\"&gt;Dungeon&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Trial\"&gt;Trial&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"Arenas%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Arena&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Creatures%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Monsters&lt;/a&gt;.\n&lt;a href=\"Major%20Aegis\"&gt;Major Aegis&lt;/a&gt;.\nTake 10% less damage from Dungeon, Trial, and Arena Monsters.\n&lt;a href=\"Minor%20Berserk\"&gt;Minor Berserk&lt;/a&gt;.\nIncreases all damage done by 5%.\n&lt;a href=\"Major%20Berserk\"&gt;Major Berserk&lt;/a&gt;.\nIncreases all damage done by 10%.\n&lt;a href=\"Minor%20Brutality\"&gt;Minor Brutality&lt;/a&gt;.\nIncreases &lt;a href=\"weapon%20damage\"&gt;weapon damage&lt;/a&gt; by 10%\n&lt;a href=\"Major%20Brutality\"&gt;Major Brutality&lt;/a&gt;.\nIncreases weapon damage by 20%\nMajor Courage.\nIncrease your &lt;a href=\"Weapon%20Damage\"&gt;Weapon&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Damage\"&gt;Spell Damage&lt;/a&gt; by 430\nMinor Courage.\nIncrease your &lt;a href=\"Weapon%20Damage\"&gt;Weapon&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Damage\"&gt;Spell Damage&lt;/a&gt; by 215\n&lt;a href=\"Empower\"&gt;Empower&lt;/a&gt;.\nIncreases damage of &lt;a href=\"Light%20attack\"&gt;light&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Medium%20attack\"&gt;medium&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"heavy%20attack\"&gt;heavy attack&lt;/a&gt;s by 40%.\nItem sets:\n&lt;a