{"id": "159805", "revid": "5064773", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=159805", "title": "Bugrol gro-Bagul", "text": "Bugrol gro-Bagul is an &lt;a href=\"Orsimer%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Orsimer&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Thief%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Thief&lt;/a&gt; who is located near the city walls of &lt;a href=\"Caldera%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Caldera&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"West%20Gash%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;West Gash&lt;/a&gt; region, where he is hiding from the city guard out in the.\nInteractions.\n&lt;a href=\"Favors%20for%20Orcs\"&gt;Favors for Orcs&lt;/a&gt;.\nWhen the &lt;a href=\"Nerevarine\"&gt;Nerevarine&lt;/a&gt; encounters Bugrol, he is hiding from the Caldera city guard, and is located near the city walls. He will ask them to deliver &lt;a href=\"Note%20from%20Bugrol\"&gt;his note&lt;/a&gt; to &lt;a href=\"Bashuk%20gra-Bat\"&gt;Bashuk gra-Bat&lt;/a&gt;, his friend, who is located within the city. Once the Nerevarine has delivered it to her, she will give them &lt;a href=\"Note%20from%20Bashuk\"&gt;her reply&lt;/a&gt; to him, which in turn they will deliver to Bugrol. As a reward, he will give them a \"useless rock,\" which is actually a &lt;a href=\"Diamond%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;diamond&lt;/a&gt;."}
