{"id": "1000786", "revid": "32045548", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=1000786", "title": "Bugsmoke", "text": "Bugsmoke is a &lt;a href=\"narcotic\"&gt;narcotic&lt;/a&gt; substance invented and primarily consumed by the &lt;a href=\"Bosmer\"&gt;Bosmer&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"Valenwood\"&gt;Valenwood&lt;/a&gt;. It is smoked on a pipe and is said to make the user feel \"strangely exhilerated.\" As per the Meat Mandate (the part of the &lt;a href=\"Green%20Pact\"&gt;Green Pact&lt;/a&gt; in which &lt;a href=\"Y%27ffre\"&gt;Y'ffre&lt;/a&gt; forbids the use of plants from Valenwood by the Bosmer in their crafts and feeding), Wood Elves cannot smoke anything of a vegetable nature, and fill their bone pipes with caterpillars or tree grubs."}
