{"id": "1694", "revid": "17401442", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=1694", "title": "Burglar", "text": "Agile, silent and curious as any feline, Burglars find the challenge of locks or an open window an irresistible target. Burglars typically slip in and out of the shadows with ease, pouches filled with treasure, finding their way into areas others thought were inaccessible. Burglars are useful when exploring new places, especially those considered highly secure.\nTo maintain stealthiness and agility necessary for their trade, burglars typically wear light armor and carry few weapons, specializing in those designed for close combat. Burglars also rarely carry shields."}
