 &lt;a href=\"Healing\"&gt;Healing&lt;/a&gt; to recover his health. Additionally, Valdimar can use &lt;a href=\"Turn%20Undead%20%28Skyrim%29\"&gt;Turn Undead&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Lesser%20Ward%20%28Skyrim%29\"&gt;Lesser Ward&lt;/a&gt;.\nValdimar's skills:"}
