{"id": "171813", "revid": "3528442", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=171813", "title": "Vale Sabre Cat", "text": "Vale Sabre Cats are hostile &lt;a href=\"Creatures%20%28Skyrim%29\"&gt;animals&lt;/a&gt; in . They can only be found in the &lt;a href=\"Forgotten%20Vale\"&gt;Forgotten Vale&lt;/a&gt; and\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Darkfall%20Cave\"&gt;Darkfall Cave&lt;/a&gt;. They can be distinguished from the regular &lt;a href=\"Sabre%20Cat%20%28Skyrim%29\"&gt;sabre cats&lt;/a&gt; by their purple and brown mottled coat and by having less fur than the other variants, making them slimmer. Additionally, vale sabre cats emit a slight purple bio-luminescence that is extinguished upon death."}
