{"id": "931914", "revid": "32045548", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=931914", "title": "Valrendil", "text": "Valrendil is an &lt;a href=\"Altmer%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Altmer&lt;/a&gt; and defector of the &lt;a href=\"Aldmeri%20Dominion%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Aldmeri Dominion&lt;/a&gt; residing next to &lt;a href=\"Deep%20Graves\"&gt;Deep Graves&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Shadowfen\"&gt;Shadowfen&lt;/a&gt;.\nBackground.\nValrendil was a Dominion military with many medals who defected his alliance to pursue a dream of decades: to revive his dead wife, &lt;a href=\"Alanya\"&gt;Alanya&lt;/a&gt;. A beautiful Altmer, she had a sudden and unavoidable death, one he could not overcome.\nHe escaped to the region of Deep Graves, southern of Shadowfen, in Black Marsh, and settled near under the permission of &lt;a href=\"Xijai-Teel\"&gt;Xijai-Teel&lt;/a&gt;. He believed the &lt;a href=\"Hist\"&gt;Hist&lt;/a&gt; would bring Alanya back to life, a task mysteriously completed. \nFor his desertion, the Aldmeri Dominion considered him a wanted &lt;a href=\"Mer\"&gt;Mer&lt;/a&gt;, placing a bounty upon his death, claiming him to be \"delusional and prone to sympathize with enemy &lt;a href=\"Argonians%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Argonians&lt;/a&gt;.\" \nLiving in a cave, completely changed into his house, he was oblivious when wisps posed a threat to the locals, leading to the events of \"&lt;a href=\"A%20Stranger%20Uninvited\"&gt;A Stranger Uninvited&lt;/a&gt;\" and \"&lt;a href=\"Broken%20Apart\"&gt;Broken Apart&lt;/a&gt;.\"\nInteractions.\n&lt;a href=\"A%20Stranger%20Uninvited\"&gt;A Stranger Uninvited&lt;/a&gt;.\n\"Xijai-Teel welcomed a traveling High Elf to Deep Graves, but she believes he has something to do with the wisps' recent aggression.\"\n&lt;a href=\"Broken%20Apart\"&gt;Broken Apart&lt;/a&gt;.\n\"To rid the area of her corrupting influence, Xijai-Teel and I cleansed the ancient vessel. We need it capture the wispmother in Deep Graves.\""}
