{"id": "3074", "revid": "32045548", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3074", "title": "Vampire Hunting", "text": "Vampire Hunting is a &lt;a href=\"Quests%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; in . Upon completing \"&lt;a href=\"Order%20of%20the%20Virtuous%20Blood%20%28Quest%29\"&gt;Order of the Virtuous Blood&lt;/a&gt;,\" one upshot is a continuing bounty of 250 for each portion of &lt;a href=\"Vampire%20Dust%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Vampire Dust&lt;/a&gt; presented to &lt;a href=\"Roland%20Jenseric\"&gt;Roland Jenseric&lt;/a&gt;.\nCombat with vampires.\nSince &lt;a href=\"Vampire%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;vampires&lt;/a&gt; are &lt;a href=\"Weakness%20to%20Fire%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;weak to fire&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Fire%20Damage%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;spells causing fire damage&lt;/a&gt; should be employed. Alternatively, &lt;a href=\"Enchanted%20Weapons%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;weapons enchanted with fire damage&lt;/a&gt; can be used. Since vampires &lt;a href=\"Resist%20Frost%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;resist frost&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Resist%20Normal%20Weapons%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;normal weapons&lt;/a&gt;, these should not be used in combat with them."}
