{"id": "1094233", "revid": "32767830", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=1094233", "title": "Vampire Knight (Online)", "text": " Vampire Knights are generic &lt;a href=\"Bretons%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Breton&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Vampire%20%28Online%29\"&gt;vampire&lt;/a&gt; residing in &lt;a href=\"Coldharbour\"&gt;Coldharbour&lt;/a&gt;. Their matriarch is &lt;a href=\"Virgar%20the%20Red\"&gt;Virgar the Red&lt;/a&gt;. They are become neutral if the &lt;a href=\"Vestige\"&gt;Vestige&lt;/a&gt; sides with Virgar and hostile if they side with &lt;a href=\"Vanus%20Galerion%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Vanus Galerion&lt;/a&gt;.\nInteractions.\n&lt;a href=\"The%20Harvest%20Heart\"&gt;The Harvest Heart&lt;/a&gt;.\nVampires occupy the Orchard beyond &lt;a href=\"the%20Chasm\"&gt;the Chasm&lt;/a&gt;, somehow empowered by &lt;a href=\"Molag%20Bal%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Molag Bal's&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Harvest%20Heart\"&gt;Harvest Heart&lt;/a&gt;. The vampires need to be dealt with before our forces can push forward toward the &lt;a href=\"Planar%20Vortex\"&gt;Planar Vortex&lt;/a&gt;."}
