{"id": "120249", "revid": "32045548", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=120249", "title": "Vampire Mage", "text": "Vampire Mage are &lt;a href=\"Bretons%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Breton&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Vampire%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;vampires&lt;/a&gt;. There are three variants, two males and one female.\nThey wear a mix of &lt;a href=\"Clothing%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;clothing&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Light%20Armor%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;light armor&lt;/a&gt; and may wield a leveled &lt;a href=\"Daggers%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;dagger&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Staves%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;staff&lt;/a&gt;. They also carry &lt;a href=\"Restore%20Health%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;restore health&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Magicka%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;restore magicka&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Potions%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;potions&lt;/a&gt;.\nVampire mages are usually found in &lt;a href=\"Caves%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;caves&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Forts%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;forts&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"Ayleid%20Ruins%20%28Oblivion%29\"&gt;Ayleid ruins&lt;/a&gt;."}
