es to the Restless League hideout to confront Basil.\nDialogue.\n\"You are wounded. Take this bandage.\" Thank you.\n\"For your good will. And my spared life.\"\nIf approached again:\n\"Come to boast of your triumph?\" Let's end it. For my sister's sake?\n\"And what of my men? What of their sake?\" Those men gave me no choice.\n\"We were attacking that ship for its known Imperial allegiance, which--\" That's your war and I'll not be drawn in.\n\"Even if you add to its casualties.\" You're still standing... Forget it, then.\n\"Cyrus. I... want to find Iszara, too.\""}
