estige and &lt;a href=\"Battlereeve%20Urcelmo\"&gt;Battlereeve Urcelmo&lt;/a&gt; about the Astanya's trap, but while she is doing this she is killed.\nDialogue.\n&lt;a href=\"Ensuring%20Security\"&gt;Ensuring Security&lt;/a&gt;.\nWhen first speaking to her:\n\"I'm sorry, I can't help you right now. I'm very busy and there's a lot to do.\"\nAfter finding the poisoned meat, if the Vestige has already helped &lt;a href=\"Advisor%20Norion\"&gt;Advisor Norion&lt;/a&gt;:\n\"Did you find anything?\"\nConversations.\n&lt;a href=\"A%20Hostile%20Situation\"&gt;A Hostile Situation&lt;/a&gt;.\nWhen entering the temple:\nBattlereeve Urcelmo: \"Mara be merciful. What's happened here?\"\nSteward Eminwe: \"You. I'm sorry. I was wrong. I tried to stop them .\u2026 Watch out. On the balcony. It's Astanya! It's a trap!\"\nWatch Captain Astanya: \"Urcelmo! I see you've met my latest toy.\"\nBattlereeve Urcelmo: \"Astanya! Traitor! Come down here and face me!\"\nWatch Captain Astanya: \"\"Our \"Queen\" has betrayed us. I wanted her head. I'll settle for yours! Kill them!\"\""}
