{"id": "1080898", "revid": "32911304", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=1080898", "title": "Sticks and Stones", "text": "Sticks and Stones was an &lt;a href=\"event%20quest\"&gt;event quest&lt;/a&gt; available in . The event launched on October 10, 2020. The quest held five difficulty settings. The next event quest was \"&lt;a href=\"The%20Eldritch%20Grotto\"&gt;The Eldritch Grotto&lt;/a&gt;\".\nBackground.\n\"Primeval forces have reshaped the monsters in the forlorn tomb found beyond the portal. No blade will pierce their skin, no element will harm them - only by using bashing weapons can I hope to defeat them.\"\nWalkthrough.\nThe event takes place in an &lt;a href=\"Ayleid\"&gt;Ayleid&lt;/a&gt; Ruin, where the &lt;a href=\"Fugitive%20%28Blades%29\"&gt;Hero&lt;/a&gt; must face off against various enemies. At the start, there are two Skeleton Sentinels blocking the way. The room after the hallway is guarded by a &lt;a href=\"Spriggan%20%28Blades%29\"&gt;Spriggan Forest Speaker&lt;/a&gt; and another Skeleton Sentinel. Proceeding up the stairs, another Spriggan Forest Speaker and &lt;a href=\"Skeleton%20%28Blades%29\"&gt;Skeleton Sentinel&lt;/a&gt; are found.\nProceeding further up the stairs, the Hero will find a large, partially caved-in, room. Here, two Skeleton Sentinels and three Spriggan Forest Speakers will have to be fought to continue. Following up the stairs, the boss is found, a unique and more deadly Skeleton Sentinel guarding a Golden Chest.\nRewards.\nThe rewards for the quest vary depending on the difficulty it is completed on:\nStage 1: Easiest.\n3 Sigils, 8 &lt;a href=\"Miscellaneous%20Items%20%28Blades%29\"&gt;Dragon Bones&lt;/a&gt;\nStage 2: Easy.\n6 Sigils, 16 Dragon Bones\nStage 3: Medium.\n12 Sigils, 32 Dragon Bones\nStage 4: Hard.\n19 Sigils, 56 Dragon Bones\nStage 5: Hardest.\n27 Sigils, 96 Dragon Bones, 36 \nSigil Shop.\nFrom the Sigils obtained for completing the event, items can be purchased in the Sigil Shop. The shop features generic equipment, but also items with bonus enchantments, ranging from one to two potential bonuses. It also features soul gems, gold, jewelry, and crafting items for alchemy, smithing, enchanting, and decorating. The shop also features the unique &lt;a href=\"Ring%20of%20Preservation%20%28Blades%29\"&gt;Ring of Preservation&lt;/a&gt;."}
