{"id": "115325", "revid": "5165253", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=115325", "title": "Stolen Reports", "text": "Stolen Reports is a &lt;a href=\"Mages%20Guild%20Quests%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Mages Guild quest&lt;/a&gt;. It can be obtained from &lt;a href=\"Ajira\"&gt;Ajira&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Balmora%20Mages%20Guild\"&gt;Balmora Mages Guild&lt;/a&gt;.\nSummary.\nSomeone has\u00a0stolen Ajira's reports, the &lt;a href=\"Ajira%27s%20Flower%20Report\"&gt;Flower Report&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"Ajira%27s%20Mushroom%20Report\"&gt;Mushroom Report&lt;/a&gt; and she suspects &lt;a href=\"Galbedir\"&gt;Galbedir's revenge&lt;/a&gt;. Galbedir has not left the guild's building, so all of\u00a0the reports are inside.\nWalkthrough.\nUpon completion of the previous quest, Ajira will tell the player that someone, probably &lt;a href=\"Galbedir\"&gt;Galbedir&lt;/a&gt;, has stolen her reports, the &lt;a href=\"Ajira%27s%20Flower%20Report\"&gt;Flower Report&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"Ajira%27s%20Mushroom%20Report\"&gt;Mushroom Report&lt;/a&gt;. She will ask the player to get them back.\nGetting Galbedir's disposition up high enough will convince her to tell the player where the reports are. Alternatively, the player may search the &lt;a href=\"Balmora%20Mages%20Guild\"&gt;Balmora Mages Guild&lt;/a&gt; themselves.\nThe Flower Report is located in the sleeping area in the basement, just around the corner from where Ajira is. It is hidden under a wardrobe.\nThe Mushroom Report is on the ground floor, in between some baskets of ingredients.\nOnce you have the reports, return to Ajira. She will tell the player she does not have any more quests for them right now, but they should return upon reaching the rank of Warlock. Until then, she suggests the player does quests for &lt;a href=\"Edwinna%20Elbert\"&gt;Edwinna Elbert&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Ald%27ruhn%20%28Morrowind%29\"&gt;Ald'ruhn&lt;/a&gt;, as she does not like &lt;a href=\"Ranis%20Athrys\"&gt;Ranis Athrys&lt;/a&gt; very much."}
