{"id": "1062588", "revid": "32911304", "url": "https://elderscrolls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=1062588", "title": "Stoneclaws", "text": "Stoneclaws is a &lt;a href=\"Khajiit%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Khajiit&lt;/a&gt; residing in the &lt;a href=\"Lilmoth%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Lilmoth&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Guild%20Hall%20%28Murkmire%29\"&gt;Guild Hall&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Murkmire\"&gt;Murkmire&lt;/a&gt; region of &lt;a href=\"Black%20Marsh%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Black Marsh&lt;/a&gt;. He is a Hall Steward and, thus, also a &lt;a href=\"Merchants%20%28Online%29\"&gt;merchant&lt;/a&gt;.\nBackground.\nStoneclaws is a Hall Steward of the Fighters Guild in the Lilmoth Guild Hall, shared by the Fighters Guild and the &lt;a href=\"Mages%20Guild%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Mages Guild&lt;/a&gt;. It is his duty as Steward to manage the Hall and assist the members within. He also facilitates armaments and equipment repairing.\nPersonality.\nStoneclaws, like many of his Fighters Guild colleagues, expresses eagerness in his desire to fight &lt;a href=\"Daedra%20%28Online%29\"&gt;Daedra&lt;/a&gt; and destroy the &lt;a href=\"Dark%20Anchors\"&gt;Dark Anchors&lt;/a&gt; impelling the &lt;a href=\"Planemeld\"&gt;Planemeld&lt;/a&gt;. As a Hall Steward, Stoneclaws is also keen on encouraging adventurers and warriors to join the Guild, including the &lt;a href=\"Vestige\"&gt;Vestige&lt;/a&gt; if they are not already a member.\nAlthough Stoneclaws believes that the lack of Daedra in Murkmire is a good thing, he also believes it leaves him with a lack of duties and opportunities for action.\nServices.\nStoneclaws offers his services as a &lt;a href=\"Merchants%20%28Online%29\"&gt;merchant&lt;/a&gt; allowing the Vestige to purchase &lt;a href=\"Weapons%20%28Online%29\"&gt;weapons&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Armor%20%28Online%29\"&gt;armor&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"repair%20kit\"&gt;repair kit&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"Items%20%28Online%29\"&gt;item&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Containers%20%28Online%29\"&gt;containers&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"Achievements%20%28Online%29\"&gt;achievement&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Furnishings%20%28Online%29\"&gt;furnishings&lt;/a&gt;. He will also buy any sellable item in the Vestige's &lt;a href=\"inventory\"&gt;inventory&lt;/a&gt; and repair damaged armor for a fee.\nDialogue.\n\"Ah, what a coincidence! I was just speaking to Hitari about the great need the Fighters Guild has for strapping adventurers, just like yourself.\""}
